Actors (might be independant):
  Actuators:
    * multiple ports
    * state?

  sensors:
    * multiple inputs

  serial lines:
    * port(s) if applicable

Device:
  * serials (port identifier string, category, e.g. ap uart)
  * actuators
     (identifier, category e.g. power, binary with state, direction)
  * sensors (identifier, category e.g. temp))
     e.g. external temperature probes
